These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, billiard, chess, whist
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, r&b, salsa, techno
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, spinach, mango, cucumber
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, blue, coral, yellow
1. the person eating spinach is the fan of techno##1
2. the person eating mango is between the person playing chess and the person playing whist##2
3. the person eating spinach is the person who likes apricot##1
4. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
5. the fan of metal is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
6. the person who likes coral is the person playing chess##1
7. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person playing whist##1
8. the person eating pineapple is on the far right##1
9. the person playing billiard is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Game   | billiard | whist   | scrabble  | chess  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | techno    | metal      | salsa    |
| Food   | cucumber | spinach | mango | pineapple |
| Color     | yellow  | apricot       | blue    | coral     |

