.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, coral, green, blue
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, cola, fanta
4 different pets are kept: bird, dog, frog, lizard
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, daffodil, iris, rose
1. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
2. the person who likes emerald is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the lizard is the person who growsdaffodil##1
4. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
5. the person drinking fanta is between the owner of the frog and the person who growsbellflower##2
6. the person who growsrose is between the person drinking fanta and the owner of the lizard##2
7. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person who likes green##1
9. the person drinking cola is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Color         | blue | coral    | green  | emerald    |
| Beverage   | 7up      | iced-tea  | fanta  | cola |
| Pet           | lizard      | frog       | dog      | bird       |
| Flower         | daffodil    | rose | iris | bellflower |

