.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, azure, coral, ivory
4 different pets are kept: turtle, dog, frog, goat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, skateboarding, tennis, parkour
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, subway
1. the person who's sport is tennis is the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person who likes coral is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the owner of the goat##1
7. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
8. the person who likes white is between the owner of the turtle and the owner of the goat##2
9. the owner of the frog is between the person who likes coral and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Color        | azure | coral     | white   | ivory     |
| Pet       | dog   | turtle   | frog | goat |
| Sport         | rugby   | tennis | parkour       | skateboarding    |
| Transport   | roller    | motorbike | helicopter  | subway    |

