 4. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the dutch##1
 5. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 6. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 7. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the fonseca-smoker is the person playing billiard##1
 9. the person eating lemon is between the american and the person playing bridge##2
10. the person playing go is the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
